Package com.ibm.as400.resource

package com.ibm.as400.resource
Deprecated Provides classes that represent IBM i resources using a generic list-based scheme.

This package has been deprecated, and is no longer being enhanced. Users are advised to use packages com.ibm.com.ibm.as400.access and com.ibm.com.ibm.as400.access.list instead.

These classes use buffering, transaction control, and list manipulation to improve the performance and manageability of lists of resources on the system.

Some of the components in the com.ibm.com.ibm.as400.access package have counterparts that are represented as resources. For example, RJobList is the com.ibm.com.ibm.as400.resource version of the JobList class in the access package.
